The paper discusses challenges and potential solutions related to iterative trial-and-error processes in data science, which involves data selection, preprocessing, transformation, and mining. These activities are closely related to several subfields of computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
